.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, azure, lavender, coral, aquamarine
There are 5 different nationalities: mexican, british, indian, colombian, dutch
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, swisher, chaman, dunhill, montecristo
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-cola, lemonade, cola, juice, sprite
5 different pets are kept: fish, cat, snake, frog, guinea-pig

1. the mexican is the person who likes white
2. the british is the owner of the fish
3. the person drinking soy-cola is the person who likes azure
4. the indian is the person drinking lemonade
5. the person who likes azure is to the right of the person who likes lavender
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the owner of the guinea-pig
7. the swisher-smoker is the person who likes coral
8. the person drinking cola is in the middle
9. the colombian is on the far left
10. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the swisher-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the frog
12. the dunhill-smoker is the person drinking juice
13. the dutch is the montecristo-smoker
14. the colombian is to the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   colombian	|    indian	|     mexican	|    british	|    dutch	|
| Color		|    coral	|      aquamarine	|      white	|     lavender	|     azure	|
| Beverage	|     sprite	|      lemonade	|      cola	| juice	|     soy-cola	|
| Cigar		|     swisher	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| dunhill	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     cat	|     frog	|     guinea-pig	|     fish	|     snake	|
